				\begin{document}$$\frac{B.Ar}{T.Ar}\cdot \frac{4}{\pi }\cdot 100$$\end{document}B.ArT.Ar·4π·100where B.Ar represent the amount of bone measured in the ROI and T.Ar the entire area of the ROI considered.
